<div><head>郭店楚簡六《魯穆公問子思》</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.2">魯穆公問於子思曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.3">「何如而可謂忠臣？」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.4">子思曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.5">「亟稱<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.6">其君之惡者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.7">可謂忠臣矣。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.8">公不悅，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.9">揖而退之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.10">成孫弋見，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.11">公曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.12">「嚮者惡問忠臣於子思，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.13">子思曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.14">『亟稱其君之惡者可謂忠<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.15">臣矣。』<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.16">寡人惑焉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.17">而未之得也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.18">成孫弋曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.19">「噫，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.20">善哉，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.21">言乎！<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.22">夫為其君之故殺其身者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.23">嘗有之矣。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.24">亟稱其君之惡者<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.25">未之有也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.26">夫為其君之故殺其身者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.27">交祿爵者也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.28">亟<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.29">稱其君之惡者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.30">遠祿爵者也，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.31">為義而遠祿爵，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.32">非<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.33">子思，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH8x4415_CHANT_001-1a.34">吾惡聞之矣。」<lb/></seg>
</p>
